	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There's a bug in the way this tool finds the fill byte, so it doesn't always use the byte with the longest run in the file. I took a look at the code, and as far as I could understand, the bug seems to be here:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">if(len&gt;=8) lens&#91;prev&#93;=len;</div><br />Should be:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">if(len&gt;=8 &amp;&amp; len &gt; lens&#91;prev&#93;) lens&#91;prev&#93;=len;</div>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


